00:19:49.280 --> 00:19:53.560
be able to compare and contrast it with the&nbsp;
other tools we covered in the previous video:&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:19:53.560 --> 00:19:58.640
Ansible, Puppet, and Chef. I hope this&nbsp;
